-- - Added and rearranged notifications
--
-- 2.0 2016-10-04 Rainer Salminen
-- - Restructured
-- - Added notification variables and events
-- - Arranged Revision History from latest to oldest
--
-- 1.3 2016-08-30 Rainer Salminen
-- - Editorial: Unified indentation and date formats in Revision History changed to ISO8601 format
-- - Added dah100FlapGroup
--
-- 1.2 25.9.2015 Perttu Fagerlund
-- - Removed dax level from this MIB file
-- - A separate TELESTE-DAX-MIB is now used as link between TELESTE-ROOT-MIB and TELESTE-DAH100-MIB
--
